Call-Light

Expertise:  Development, Support & Maintenance

Platforms:   Website & Admin Panel

Get In Touch

Overview of the Project

Overview of the Project

Call-Light redefines home healthcare by offering an unparalleled blend of safety, simplicity, and affordability in hiring a nurse or clinician. Our platform ensures that top-notch healthcare comes to you, wherever you are, eliminating the need to navigate complex healthcare systems or wait in long queues. We handpick our professionals for their expertise and dedication to compassion, making sure that you or your loved ones receive the care and attention deserved. With Call-Light, peace of mind is just a click away, because we believe that quality healthcare should be as accessible and straightforward as turning on a light.

The Challenge

The Challenges We Faced

Integrating APIs was tough as it involved linking outside data with our system. Also, checking nurses’ IDs through CNIC (Computerized National Identity Card) required automation to streamline the process and maintain accuracy.

Our Approach

Innovative and User-Centric Development

At Hashlogics, we adopt an innovative and user-centric approach to home healthcare solutions. We prioritize simplicity, efficiency, and continuous improvement to empower individuals and families in accessing quality care.

Redefining Healthcare Experience

Personalized Engagement

Every interaction with Call-Light is customized to meet your unique healthcare needs to ensure a personalized experience.

Easy Access

Our platform brings professionals directly to you by eliminating the need for navigating complex healthcare systems or waiting in long queues.

Ensuring Safety and Security

Handpicked Professionals
Experienced and compassionate nurses and clinicians are listed to ensure that you and your loved ones receive the best care.
Strict Privacy Protocols

We prioritize your privacy with strict security measures and privacy protocols to protect your personal information at every step.

Continuous Innovation

Innovative Solutions

We use advanced technology to redefine home healthcare, setting new benchmarks for reliability and accessibility.

User Feedback Integration

 Your feedback is valuable to us. We actively seek feedback to make enhancements that directly benefit your operations.

Solution - CareSeeker

Clients choose nurses

Call-Light helps clients easily find and hire private nurses and clinicians for short-term or long-term care. All Call-Light care providers are vetted and highly experienced across a variety of specialties, from newborn to geriatric care.

Care Provider

Nurses choose clients

Nurses have complete freedom to set their own hours, rates, and whether to accept or decline a job opportunity. All communications, bookings, and payment are managed directly through the Call-Light app.

Catering to Diverse Healthcare Needs

Call-Light caters to a diverse range of healthcare requirements, serving individuals seeking routine check-ups to those requiring specialized care. This section will profile typical users, illustrating how the platform addresses their unique healthcare needs and challenges.

Emily

Age: 35

Business Type

Emily is a seasoned entrepreneur in the healthcare sector, specifically managing a network of home care agencies that provide personalized nursing.

Business Type

Emily’s main goal is to efficiently manage her store’s inventory, generate invoices for customers, and understand her sales performance.

Goals

Emily’s main goal is to efficiently manage her store’s inventory, generate invoices for customers, and understand her sales performance.

Pain Points

Difficulty in efficiently matching the right nurse with the right patient based on specific care needs and nurse qualifications.

How Call-light Helps

  • Clients (or their families) can effortlessly select nurses based on specific care requirements, credentials, and reviews.
  • Nurses have the autonomy to choose clients, allowing for a better match based on expertise, location, and schedule preferences.
  • The platform’s intuitive interface reduces administrative burdens, making the process of scheduling and managing care more efficient.
  • Call-Light’s commitment to security and privacy aligns with Emily’s need to maintain high standards of data protection and regulatory compliance.
